%% ETHAGT04 — Espectro do raciocínio (simplicidade vs custo)
flowchart LR
    Simple["Simples<br/>CoT (1 chamada)"] --> Medium["Médio<br/>ReAct / Plan-Execute"]
    Medium --> Complex["Complexo<br/>ToT / LATS / Reflexion"]
    Complex --> Frontier["Fronteira<br/>Reasoning model nativo"]
    Simple -.custo.-> Low(["$ barato"])
    Frontier -.custo.-> High(["$$$ caro"])
    Simple -.accuracy.-> LowA(["básica"])
    Frontier -.accuracy.-> HighA(["máxima"])

    classDef s fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#15803d,color:#000
    classDef m fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#1e40af,color:#000
    classDef c fill:#fed7aa,stroke:#c2410c,color:#000
    classDef f fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#be185d,color:#000
    class Simple s
    class Medium m
    class Complex c
    class Frontier f
